These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
Flower: aconite, zinnia, balloon-flower, lily
Pet: cat, ferret, lizard, turtle
Transport: jet-ski, snowmobile, trike, van
1. Transport:trike is on the left of Pet:ferret##1
2. Transport:van == Pet:cat##1
3. Flower:balloon-flower is on the far left##1
4. Flower:aconite is on the far right##1
5. Pet:ferret is between Transport:trike and Flower:zinnia##2
6. Transport:snowmobile == Pet:lizard##1
7. Pet:cat is on the right of Pet:ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Flower        | balloon-flower | lily  | zinnia | aconite  |
| Pet         | turtle    | ferret  | cat       | lizard     |
| Transport   | trike     | jet-ski | van       | snowmobile |

