2. Sport:climbing is on the right of Hobby:chess##1
3. Sport:sailing is on the far left##1
4. Sport:swimming is between Color:fuchsia and Hobby:reading##2
5. Color:fuchsia == Sport:sailing##1
6. Color:blood-red is on the left of Sport:climbing##1
7. Color:black == Sport:surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | drawing | chess    | reading  | magic-tricks |
| Color   | fuchsia  | blood-red  | grey   | black    |
| Sport         | sailing | swimming | climbing | surfing      |

